===Proper noun===
'''Ali'''

# a male [[given name]], derived from the [[Arabic]] root '''`-l-y''' which means "high"
# the [[Muslim]] [[caliph]] [[Wikipedia:Ali|Ali ibn Abi Talib]], the [[assasination]] of whom led to the [[schism]] between [[Sunni]] and [[Shiite]] branches. Arabic:(علي بن ابي طالب)
# a [[Muslim]] [[surname]]
# a [[nickname]] surrogate for [[Alison]], [[Alyson]], [[Allyson]] or [[Allison]]
# a 2001 [[biopic]] on [[w:Muhammed Ali|Muhammed Ali]]

